{"tid":1312131,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"十一哥，小心啲囖，咪亂入細路被窩","createTime":"2019-07-13T12:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T00:37:34.000Z","uid":107623,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0769e8fcc2b657192563869ebca82ad94649a3bc","tid":1312131,"uid":107623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"十一哥，戲子一個，<br />\r\n往日是最純阿哥。<br />\r\n到老婆娶左，有仔一個，<br />\r\n淫慾漸開始猛火。<br />\r\n(年長左 時光飛過 老年漸想出吓火)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n老藕學去搵野食，漸發現細路至激。<br />\r\n處女就最高價值，驊大狀拼命尋覓。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n十一哥，小心啲囖，<br />\r\n咪亂入細路被窩。<br />\r\n但極緊火，雪廠經過，<br />\r\n人慾望相當赤裸。<br />\r\n(佢閒錢多 雪廠經過 有慾望就出吓火)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n老驥係最識食，佢漠視法律意識。<br />\r\n性愛叛社會價值，老共特務拍下行歷。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n十一哥，好色之過，<br />\r\n佢亂入細路被窩。<br />\r\n唉！黃撚左，無陰公囖，<br />\r\n投共避法律橫禍。<br />\r\n(人之初，應知錯，唔自重就鑄下情禍)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n佢繼續會搵野食，傳媒問及塊面變色。<br />\r\n撐老共佢積極，全力延長快樂權力。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n十一哥，雪廠經過，<br />\r\n叫傳媒勿過分揣摩。<br />\r\n喂十一哥，小心啲囖，<br />\r\n以避日後再遇橫禍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次改歌，<br />\n唔岩音請大家幫我改好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb45025467b1090637a073bce383718ea55b2068","tid":1312131,"uid":107623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ac70d3f5d8db2e24644badc5b3e6df7c8bf4e3","tid":1312131,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"又幾好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98dc900d8a96aedbdc083e501018a38e51a2a4e","tid":1312131,"uid":210088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99dcca544a3e773d76cb8ef748e22b84dfb88d9b","tid":1312131,"uid":148987,"like":0